      "text": [
        " يَا أَمِيرَ اَلْمُؤْمِنِينَ إِنِّي طَلَّقْتُ اِمْرَأَتِي فَقَالَ \"أَ لَكَ بَيِّنَةٌ\" فَقَالَ لاَ فَقَالَ \"اُعْزُبْ\"."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.4756 - A man came to the Commander of the Faithful (as) and said:\n\"O Commander of the Faithful, I have divorced my wife.\"\nImam (as) asked: \"Do you have any evidence (witnesses)?\"\nThe man replied: \"No.\"\nSo Imam (as) said: \"Be gone (uʿzub).\""
        ]
      }
    },
